      <title>谈判失败，贸易陷入混乱，加拿大铁路公司将工人拒之门外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/canada-railways-lock-out-workers-as-talks-fail-snarling-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大两条最大的铁路公司（占全国铁路网的近 80%）于周四凌晨因与工会谈判失败而关闭，此举立即阻断了每天运输约 10 亿加元（7.4 亿美元）贸易的北美供应链主干道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/canada-railways-lock-out-workers-as-talks-fail-snarling-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 04:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前韩国央行高级副行长就利率决策发表讲话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-22/former-bok-senior-deputy-governor-on-rate-decision-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行维持基准利率不变。崇实大学经济学教授、前韩国央行高级副行长李承宪表示，韩国房地产市场和美联储的决定将决定韩国央行的未来走向。他在“彭博社：中国秀”节目中与 Shery Ahn 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-22/former-bok-senior-deputy-governor-on-rate-decision-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 04:27:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
